{"tid":851384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【芬佬FAT FAT】強積金資產逾8600億元　約相當於政府財政儲備八成","createTime":"2018-10-07T05:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T06:14:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62c8fb96e43c1b045097204e822d0834895408a5","tid":851384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1421695_1_L_20181007112652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1421695_1_L_20181007112652.jpg&h=3e50099f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n積金局主席黃友嘉說，強積金制度實施以來，積金局為僱員討回合共超過20億元強積金供款及附加費，強積金現時的資產已超過8600億元，大約相當於政府財政儲備的八成。<br />\n<br />\n黃友嘉在網誌表示，上月是積金局成立20周年，局方多年來一直致力打擊僱主違規行為，積極跟進所有涉嫌拖欠供款的個案，代僱員追討欠款，並將違規個案轉交警方或律政司以提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，積金局過去推出不同措施推動受託人調低收費，包括要求受託人以劃一方式披露基金收費資料、精簡強積金計劃的行政程序、推出低收費基金，以及合併效率較低的計劃和基金等。<br />\n<br />\n黃友嘉說目前400多個基金，已有近100個基金的開支比率是1%或以下，基金開支比率由2007年12月的2.1%下降至目前的1.53%，下調幅度近三成。<br />\n<br />\n他指出近年積金局積極推動強積金行政程序標準化、簡化和自動化，正籌備中央電子平台「積金易」，以及加強宣傳，鼓勵僱主和計劃成員善用科技，期望強積金制度能進行數碼轉型。"},{"pid":"625e6c4b7b43ac55c97385c9abcb0101d57d1cb3","tid":851384,"uid":40779,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強姦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"264959f51596469509642241bbc60c0bca92a35a","tid":851384,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又想玩d乜, 大佬呢d $全部係小市民收入到扣返黎"},{"pid":"454ecf049a33a8416c443601bb9e868defdbedbe","tid":851384,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"咁大筆錢，又可以為国家捐驅了"},{"pid":"a5836c133277cfaed5084f2f93b865553e68a6c8","tid":851384,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"俾支那幫港豬投資咪唔洗益班基金佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏國又贏"},{"pid":"a3630cadb30989352b978a14c925b76e42b4a387","tid":851384,"uid":78938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"其實最發達係d強積金計劃管理公司，唔係基金公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7661e33dc4cfe9fe8fecac935b8b768dc32eaef","tid":851384,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"萬億儲備倒落海(中國建人工島)<br />\n萬億強姦金買中國公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要垃圾同股不同權<br />\n全面救國打貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb2c7e2badf8b01838b219ecda0087317f62d81","tid":851384,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"拎去填海啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad22b8e04a17a8b5a348baf1fcea3ce5d094657","tid":851384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"8600億元一齊棄港支股票, 轉美股會點？<br />\n<br />\n你轉美股越轉得遲, 就越蝕得多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}